# Run example end-to-end

```{r anna-test}
outputFolder <- "output"
fp_exp <- fragpipe_data$design
fp_proteins <- fragpipe_data$intensities

IntensityExperiment <- runGenericDiscovery(experimentDesign = fp_exp, proteinIntensities = fp_proteins)

writeProteinViz(outputFolder = outputFolder, IntensityExperiment=IntensityExperiment)
```
